{"id": "duc04-testb-47:6#19", "contents": "Chechen Deputy Prime Minister Turpal Atgeriyev said authorities had arrested a man who confessed to kidnapping the four foreigners. The suspect was identified as Apti Abitayev. Chechen security forces were searching Friday for additional suspects as well as the bodies of the four foreigners. Atgeriyev also commented on a videotape that showed one of the four victims, Peter Kennedy, saying he was spying for Britain. Atgeriyev stated that he did not place any value in the tape, suggesting that certain methods might have forced Kennedy to confess to any crime."}
